                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-646-18390204 t18390204-646-punishment-105"></join>Confined Two Years</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">HANNAH THORNE</hi>—<hi rend="largeCaps">
                     <rs id="t18390204-646-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
